WarehouseGlobalLedgerDistributionReport is an ActionForm
    action is WarehouseGlobalLedgerDistributionReport
    Layout
        paragraph
            Company
            Company.Name
                no label
                display as text
        paragraph
            Location
                select is ProductionLocations
            Location.Name
                no label
                display as text
        two column distributed
            FrWorkOrder
                label is "FromWorkOrder"
            ToWorkOrder
                label is "ToWorkOrder"
        two column distributed
            FrGlDate
                label is "FromPostingDate"
            ToGlDate
                label is "ToPostingDate"
        single column
            ReportOption
        header2 of untranslatable:"Report Distribution"
        two column distributed
            column1 of 40%
                WarehouseGlobalLedgerDistributionReportReport_RDG
            column2 of 25%
                WarehouseGlobalLedgerDistributionReportReport_XPT
